        Creates an arrow
        Parameters:
        x - the x-coordinate of the upper-left corner of the enclosing rectangle
        y - the y-coordinate of the upper-left corner of the enclosing rectangle
        width - the width of the enclosing rectangle
        height - the height of the enclosing rectangle
        horizontal - if true, the arrow points left or right; if false, the arrow points up or down
        left - if true, the arrow points left or down; if false, the arrow points right or up
        headOffset - the number of pixels the arrowhead will stretch back, relative to the start of the line
        foreground - the color of the arrow
        background - the color of the rest of the enclosing rectangle
